title: Fatuberlio Administrative Post
content:
Fatuberlio, officially Fatuberlio Administrative Post (Portuguese: Posto Administrativo de Fatuberlio, Tetum: Postu administrativu Fatu-Berliu), is an administrative post (and was formerly a subdistrict) in the Manufahi municipality of East Timor.[1][2] Its seat or administrative centre is ClacucÂ [de].[2]
